org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.targets

Interface ITargetAttributes

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NilTargetAttributes, TargetAttributesMap, TargetAttributesMetadata

    public interface ITargetAttributes
    Attributes that changes the target output, such as "frame rate", "SWF width" and "Use GPU". The values come from either special attributes on the main MXML document or the [SWF] metadata tag in the main ActionScript class.
